if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_transbox')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_transbox
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_transbox */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_transbox (
boxID int not null,
boxcode nvarchar(20) null,
tranID int null,
packgenum int null,
isstock int null,
StockNub int null,
apptime datetime null,
constraint PK_BUSI_TRANSBOX primary key (boxID)
)
go
